# SoundPlayer Todo List

## Authentication & Error Handling
- [ ] Add a "Retry Connection" button when authentication fails.
- [ ] Store Spotify credentials securely using a configuration file or environment variables instead of hardcoding.
- [ ] Handle token expiration gracefully without requiring a full restart.

## Playback Features
- [ ] Implement volume control (increment/decrement with keys).
- [ ] Add a progress bar for the currently playing track.
- [ ] Implement "Shuffle" and "Repeat" toggle functionality.
- [ ] Show album art (if possible in TUI using ASCII/Unicode or a supported terminal protocol).

## UI/UX Enhancements
- [ ] Add a search bar to filter playlists or songs.
- [ ] Implement sorting for the song table (by title, artist, or album).
- [ ] Add notifications for track changes.
- [ ] Improve the sidebar with icons or more detailed playlist info (e.g., track count).

## Technical Debt & Performance
- [ ] Refactor Spotify API calls into a dedicated service class.
- [ ] Add unit tests for the playback logic and data parsing.
- [ ] Implement caching for playlist data to reduce API calls.
